resources.residConnectUpsellFlyoutText: Ungabona iifoto neevidiyo ukusuka kwiizixhobo zakho, iisevisi kunye neenethiweki zoluntu endaweni enye.  Ukuqalisa, qinisekisa ukuba uqhagamshele kwi-intanethi.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_EmptySourceView: Yonke imithombo yeefoto zakho ifihlakele. Ukubonisa eminye, tshintsha iisetingi zakho.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Usetyenziso lweMifanekiso lubonisa iifoto zakho neevidiyo ezivela kwezinye izixhobo kwindawo enye.

Ukuze ubone okuqulethweyo kwezinye iPC, yiya kulo PCSkyDrive.com/windows ukuze ukhuphele ufakele iMicrosoft SkyDrive, sayina ungene ngeakhwunti yakho yeMicrosoft, uze uqinisekise ukuba ukhetha Landa iifayile zakho naphi na iisetingi.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: Ukuba unazo, qiniseka ukuba uziquke kwilayibhrari yeMifanekiso yakho{{%1}}.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
I-SkyDrive sikunika indawo yokugcina simahla iifoto, iividiyo namaxwebhu ukuze uwafumane naphi na. r

Yiya SkyDrive.comukuze uqale. Naziphi na iifoto neevidiyo ozigcinileyo ziza kuboniswa apha.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Ukuze uqale, qhagamshelisa isixhobo (ikhamera, ifowuni, i-USB flash drive, njl.) uzingenise okanye uzikhupele kwiifoto kunye neevidiyo kwilayibrari yeMifanekiso yakho.

Ukuba uneefoto okanye iividiyo kule PC, qiniseka ukuba ziqukiwe kwilayibbrari yeMifanekiso yakho. Unako ukulawula ilayibhrari yakho yeMifanekiso kwiFile Explorer.
resources.residErrorSourceUnavailableMessageFmt: Usenakho ukubona ezinye iifoto neevidiyo, kodwa mhlawumbi hayi ezamva nje. Uhlaziyo lokugqibela belu {{%1}}.

resources.residErrorServiceRemovedInstructionFmt: {{%1}} ayisaqhagamshelwanga kwiakhawunti ye-Microsoft. Ukuba ufuna ukuhlala usibona isiqulatho esisuka ku- {{%1}}, qhagamshela kwakhona.
resources.residErrorDeviceOfflineInstructionText: Yiya ku {{%1}} uqinisekisa ukuba ilayitiwe kwaye iqhagamshele kwi-intanethi. Tepha okanye cofa iayikhon yeSkyDrive kwindawo yesaziso (ekupheleni ngasekunene kwetaskbha), khetha Iisetingi, uqinisekise i- Thatha iifayile isetingi ikhethiwe kwi- Jikelel kwithebhu.
